Adaptation.title: Hunter x Hunter: Greed Island Final

background: Hunter x Hunter has been published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump Advanced imprint since April 5, 2005; in Spanish by Panini Comics since October 2012; and in Brazilian Portuguese by Jbc since January 2008.The series has been serialized irregularly since 2006 due to Yoshihiro Togashi's health problems.
synopsis: Hunters are a special breed, dedicated to tracking down treasures, magical beasts, and even other men. But such pursuits require a license, and less than one in a hundred thousand can pass the grueling qualification exam. Those who do pass gain access to restricted areas, amazing stores of information, and the right to call themselves Hunters. (Source: Shonen Jump)
title: Hunter x Hunter
